Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.85,futureqestionaire_00:00,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Future Plans Questionnaire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.85,ycnn_00:00,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Year    Class    Number   Name
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.85,question_00:00,Text,0000,0000,0000,,1. What would you like to do after graduation? (Circle your answer.)\N1 Go to college  2 Get a job  3 Undecided  4 Other
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.85,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Which course are you guys going for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.22,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hina and I are probably \Ngoing into liberal arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:07.01,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko's still thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:10.01,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Maybe I'll go with \Nliberal arts, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.08,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:14.58,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I've kinda decided, but I'll \Ngive it some more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.91,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think I should do, Hayato-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:20.02,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.36,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You need to give it some serious thought, \Nor you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.81,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.23,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hayato-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:27.92,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,is it true you're going \Nout with Yukinoshita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.46,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.32,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Who said something irresponsible like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.26,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:38.88,Ore_Main,Ohoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.56,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.75,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear about Hayama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.73,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw them together over winter break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.61,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems like the \Nreal deal, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.63,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:24.49,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with where I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.58,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.58,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.58,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So your birthday is January 3rd, \NYukinoshita-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.87,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, mine is April 16th, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:40.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you even here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.46,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.77,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually a little \Nfavor I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:54.06,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita-senpai, are you really \Ngoing out with Hayama-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.28,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:01.74,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.12,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.37,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That obviously isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.40,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.25,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was no way it could be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.91,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when you went out the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.57,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like someone saw that \Nand got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.38,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The petty suspicions of a lowlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.06,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know... They say a \Nrumor only lasts 49 days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's 75 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.51,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.64,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-senpai's never had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:31.67,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,any rumors specifically about \Nhim before, weirdly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.02,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,He's, like, everybody's Hayama Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:37.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,So since this rumor came up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.94,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,there are more people \Ntrying to mess with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.35,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like girls confessing to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.33,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,or if they don't go that far, they try \Nto appeal to him by "just checking."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.52,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Checking? On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.25,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,And that appeals to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.95,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out with anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.47,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:10.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.30,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.73,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's just an issue of how you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.42,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't say that \Nwouldn't appeal to me, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.84,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it sure as hell did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.57,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.27,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, anyway, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what's going on with Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I understand very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.86,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Those really do look great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.74,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:48.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.35,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.96,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Did you always wear glasses, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.21,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,These reduce blue light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.07,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should try a pair of those, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look at the computer that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.96,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I look at it all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.00,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon, let me see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.82,yumikosatotaku,Text,0000,0000,0000,,YUMIKO☆san\NSATOSATO-san\NTakurou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.31,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.15,Notitle_05:10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Title
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:13.15,deciding_05:10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,How is everyone deciding whether to pick liberal arts or sciences?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.04,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.02,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:31.99,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I appreciate your help with the \Nfuture plans counseling sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No one told us about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.95,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.86,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'd you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.00,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something going on with you and Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.38,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.91,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other since \Nwe were young. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.16,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.41,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Would lying benefit me in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.59,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing has always annoyed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.89,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why do you have to talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.74,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.42,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I really hate that about y—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I already explained that to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.26,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,They just bumped into each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.93,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.70,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all it was, \NHayato wouldn't be so bothered by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.45,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.23,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.23,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,something a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.66,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Even if something did happen, \Nand I told you all about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.49,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,would it change anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.00,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, and everyone else, believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.25,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.80,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That part of you seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.26,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else you'd like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, calm down. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You, too. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.40,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I am calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.98,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:09.44,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the people closest to \Nme understand, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.60,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously. That's exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.54,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about the people closest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.28,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to be. \NThat's why I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.58,Notitle_05:10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,No Title
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.58,deciding_05:10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,How is everyone deciding whether to pick liberal arts or sciences?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:27.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What you want to know isn't what \Nhappened a long time ago, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:31.22,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I... just... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:32.72,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.72,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,thought it'd be nice if we could \Nbe together a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.49,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,All of us, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:45.11,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato's been distant lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:48.45,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Even I realize this is weird, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.99,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.99,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.43,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:59.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to want to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.83,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Miura probably wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:09.13,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,what future course Hayama will take, \Nand what he'll do beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:13.31,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And she knows things can't \Nstay the way they are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.68,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But that just makes her want to \Nstay close to him all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.10,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Miura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the fact that he won't tell anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,mean that he doesn't want anyone to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He might not like being asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:27.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.48,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.02,Ore_Main,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.14,Ore_Main,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.54,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only choice I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.92,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.17,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Already using them, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.33,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't feel right \Nleaving it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.06,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it'll be easier to \Nask him alone. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... Sorry to leave it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.30,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. Work is work, can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.82,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.07,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,My future plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.20,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone ask you to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, just... for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.96,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Then can I ask you a favor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.79,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop being so intrusive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:36.26,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,If I said something contrary \Nlike that, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.30,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd cross that bridge when the time came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.63,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.56,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,As for your question,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.42,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the answer to your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.25,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Future plans, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.49,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've been playing tennis for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.42,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd like something related to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get a recommendation \Nor something, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.15,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Only a precious few get those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.17,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,At our school, only someone like \NHayama-kun would have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.54,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.28,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,See you after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.29,Ore_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.02,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't suit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:13.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No... I just didn't know you did \Ncaptain-ish stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It surprised me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.30,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing a pretty solid job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.80,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I might be a little unreliable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I could rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:25.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'd know yet, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty sure I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.38,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:36.44,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.95,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And... you guys, too! Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.19,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello, Iroha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.45,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,We have to rearrange all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the alumni came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Alumni?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.38,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Hikigaya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.25,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.05,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, there's something \NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.18,winterevent_11:01,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Soubu High's Annual Winter Event
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.18,marathon_11:01,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Marathon Race!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.18,blah_11:01,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's not that you're weak. \NI'm just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.51,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato's future plans? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.35,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought you could handle \Nthings on your own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.00,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are relying on others again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:15.19,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That was cute when you \Nwere little, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.17,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.75,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.95,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Walk me to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:37.96,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often you get a chance to walk \Nhome with a gorgeous older girl like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.80,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.66,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard which curriculum \NYukino-chan wants to go into?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.53,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.40,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess she wouldn't \Nvolunteer the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.76,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you ask her, okay, Hikigaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.54,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll check each other's answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you'd call that \N"checking each other's answers."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:04.24,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the little details!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.58,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you try \Nasking Hayato directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:11.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He said some stuff, \Nbut wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.36,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.33,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato was hoping for it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.34,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:20.38,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,For someone to find him... maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's Hayama Hayato, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.14,Ore_Flashback,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the good guy you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.14,Ore_Italics,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to call this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.28,Ore_Italics,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I need a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:00.74,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-senpai! Good luck going \Nfor your second consecutive win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.88,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayato... g-good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.57,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,And good luck to you, too, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.64,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,No, not you, Tobe-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.01,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.44,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.70,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.37,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.37,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm glad I ride a bike to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.76,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's no way \NI could run this long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.66,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you're keeping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I don't think about pacing \Nmyself, it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:23.30,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how people feel as they \Napproach a halfway point in a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.33,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do they despair at the knowledge \Nthat half the trial still remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.21,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Or do they feel relieved to \Nhave made it halfway through?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.80,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Most would probably feel one of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:36.99,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And both of those emotions create \Nopenings in people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:40.47,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've pushed myself this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:45.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Was Miura handy for keeping girls away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Was she useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.74,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pick liberal arts or sciences?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.43,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me put it another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Pick sciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.25,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know which one you had chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But it can still be changed, so change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to meet your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.80,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to stop being intrusive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:21.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,you want to stop being the \NHayama Hayato everyone wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you go with sciences, \Nthere won't be as many people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and there aren't many girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:35.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can put distance between you and \Nthe problems intruding in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if your choice doesn't match theirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,they'll all accept it and \Ndrift away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it ends naturally, nobody gets hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and you won't have to betray \Nanyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.03,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I was right. We never could've been friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.12,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.98,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.82,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I feel inferior to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.28,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't stand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.25,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted us to be equals,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.39,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,so I could accept losing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.12,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:27.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for blocking your \Nsecond consecutive win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:30.38,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll win. That's what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.67,Ore_Main,Hayamae,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.18,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:53.15,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Hayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.66,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I knew for sure you'd win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:04.01,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to finish the race \Nthanks to all of your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.81,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.36,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:09.95,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.63,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.39,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! A round of applause for Hayama-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to announce who \Nplaced after him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.77,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So he wasn't really going \Nout with Yukinoshita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.53,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess rumors are just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.70,nurse_17:33,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.68,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.56,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped to rest for a bit, \Nand they made me forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.58,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hurt yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.83,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You could've had them treat it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No one was there by the time \NI crossed the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.21,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I guess it was bad timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.12,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's your luck that was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.71,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe your eyes, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,My personality, my pride... \NA lot of me is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.94,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your hands don't \Nwork so well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.49,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I can do this much by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.78,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... That stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.74,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that. It's to kill the germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.72,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It only makes sense that it \Nwould be effective on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop treating me like a germ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.22,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like you were \Nrunning with Hayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.91,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get any answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:44.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, he's not \Ngoing into sciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.10,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That's a funny way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.08,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.52,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.64,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:25.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask which course you're going into?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.63,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time you've \Nasked me a question like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:29.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.19,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,For what it's worth, \NI'll be going into liberal arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.74,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.78,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, we'll all stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in terms of categories, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna head back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:49.96,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.29,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:19:58.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:03.89,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah... I just got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:07.04,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon, sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.47,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko and the gang are \Ngoing to the after-party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:11.76,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.73,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble that \Ncrazy rumor caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.09,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't particularly trouble me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:22.15,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.07,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful that you were concerned for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.95,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.26,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that so many things \Nare different from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.80,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon! The food's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.78,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's all these chickens! \NAnd they're totally cooked whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.28,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She really has changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.53,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's not chasing \NHaruno-san's shadow anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.79,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:03.60,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:04.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Noticed what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.52,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you don't know, \NI guess that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.04,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. There's something \NI forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:15.37,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Things like moving up to the next grade
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.31,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,or to college don't reset relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that totally does reset them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.82,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's only for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.88,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You and I aren't the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.55,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then why wouldn't you tell anyone \Nwhich course you're going into?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:29.91,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,If I chose something because \NI had no other choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.22,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't call it my own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.93,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:51.41,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You might be the first person \Nwho ever said that to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.49,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.19,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I won't choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.19,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.75,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that's the best way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.71,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama Hayato\N\NAlways Responds to Everyone's Expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.58,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It's my self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:24:08.63,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#12 Still, The Thing He Seeks Is Out of Reach, And He Continues to Mistake What's Real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:42.80,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Hayato's going into liberal arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.62,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I'll do that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.68,Ore_Main_Top,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should make \Nthat decision so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.35,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I particularly want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.50,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can put off starting college, \Nbut this doesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:55.22,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be tough to put up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.31,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't need to hear \Nthat from you, Hikio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.32,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,And, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:05.17,Ore_Main_Top,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I think all of him is cool, \Nincluding his troublesome side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:06.43,Ore_Main_Top,?,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.63,Ore_Main_Top,?,0000,0000,0000,,It could've been that much simpler...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.63,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
